  <scopecontent id="aspace_5e2da66d358c98670fd5c161a669060a" encodinganalog="520$b">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>These papers represent drafts of several of Gipson's short stories, screenplays, and one nonfiction autobiographical piece, arranged by genre and in chronological order, with dates ranging from 1948-1957, and many items having no date. For each item there is typically one annotated typescript and one final draft typescript, along with a custom made folding box for the items related to each title. Of particular note is the 1957 shooting script for the Walt Disney film production of Gipson's <emph render="italic">Old Yeller</emph>, which also includes a letter from Gipson to Joe Small.</p>  </scopecontent>
